OL,3,CPlans for #24 million airport upgrade
OL,4,Crecommended for approval
OL,6,FThe long-running debate on whether 's
OL,7,Fdeteriorating runway will be rebuilt
OL,8,Fhas taken a step forward with an
OL,9,Findependent planning officer .
OL,11,FTheir report has highlighted some
OL,12,Fconcerns, including how building work
OL,13,Fcould impact local historical sites
OL,14,Fand wildlife such as bats.
OL,16,FHowever, they concluded that
OL,17,F"ultimately the benefits are
OL,18,Fconsidered to clearly and demonstrably
OL,19,Foutweigh the harms".
