OL,3,CPlans for #24 million airport upgrade
OL,4,Crecommended for approval
OL,6,FThe review was published after a
OL,7,Fmeeting of Alderney States on
OL,8,FWednesday 15 May.
OL,10,FThe island's Development Committee
OL,11,Fwill now have the final say on whether
OL,12,For not to grant planning permission on
OL,13,FThursday 30 May.
OL,15,FGuernsey's government has already
OL,16,Fallocated #24 million for the project
OL,17,Fbut if it ends up costing more
OL,18,Ffollowing the tender process, the
OL,19,Fplans may need to go back to Guernsey
OL,20,FStates again for approval.
