OL,6,FAlderney Airport timeline:
OL,8,FThe runway has been repaired in the
OL,9,Fmeantime but many Alderney residents
OL,10,Fhave become increasingly frustrated
OL,11,Fwith the patchwork state of the
OL,12,Fasphalt and continuing delays to a
OL,13,Fmore permanent solution.
OL,15,FThe head of Guernsey's States Trading
OL,16,FSupervisory Board says that a
OL,17,Fcontractor to carry out the work has
OL,18,Fbeen decided but a final figure is yet
OL,19,Fto be settled on.
